The paper deals with deep probabilistic generative models, specifically Variational Auto-encoders (VAE), and proposes a new method for detecting out-of-distribution (OOD) samples. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE), and Cryptography and Security (cs.CR) as OOD detection is an important problem in these fields.
